headline: Nasdaq Maintains Over a Decade of Listings Leadership in 2025
summary: Largest Exchange Transfer in History & Biggest IPO of the Year Highest Capital Raised Since 2021 - $46.65 Billion Raised NEW YORK, Dec. 18, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Nasdaq (Nasdaq: NDAQ) announced today that in 2025 it raised a total of $46.65 billion from new listings, marking the strongest year for capital raise since 2021.
